    <item>
      <title>中国对夜间骑行热潮的管制出现逆转，显示出对控制的痴迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/china-u-turn-on-night-biking-craze-shows-obsession-with-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[夜间骑车热潮引发中国官员的强烈反对，他们担心这会造成交通混乱，而大学生的突然大规模骑行也让他们措手不及——而大学生群体素来有抗议的历史。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/china-u-turn-on-night-biking-craze-shows-obsession-with-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 10:47:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国将于 2025 年部署以色列的“箭式”防御系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/germany-set-to-deploy-israel-s-arrow-defense-system-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列称，其“箭式”先进防空系统将于明年部署在德国，这表明尽管一年来经历了多条战线的战斗，但其史上最大武器出口协议仍进展顺利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/germany-set-to-deploy-israel-s-arrow-defense-system-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 10:29:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NHK 称日本经济刺激计划将包括降价措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/japan-s-stimulus-package-to-include-price-relief-steps-nhk-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据日本放送协会（NHK）报道，日本新的经济刺激计划将包括发放现金以帮助低收入家庭应对通货膨胀，并提供额外资金用于防灾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/japan-s-stimulus-package-to-include-price-relief-steps-nhk-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 10:17:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毛里求斯领导人承认选举失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/mauritian-prime-minister-jugnauth-concedes-election-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛里求斯总理普拉温德·库马尔·贾格纳特在周日的选举中承认失败，因为初步结果显示，他所领导的五党联盟“联盟列佩普”落后于其主要竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/mauritian-prime-minister-jugnauth-concedes-election-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 10:15:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据报道，泰国将任命批评者为央行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/thailand-to-name-central-bank-critic-as-bot-chair-reports-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国将任命前财政部长基迪拉特纳拉农 (Kittiratt Na-Ranong) 为新任泰国央行行长，这一迹象表明泰国政府试图加强对央行的控制，泰国央行与泰国政府在货币政策和通胀目标方面存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/thailand-to-name-central-bank-critic-as-bot-chair-reports-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 09:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博茨瓦纳领导人选择副总理 Gaolathe 担任财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/botswana-s-president-picks-deputy-gaolathe-as-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博茨瓦纳新任领导人杜马博科公布了六名内阁成员名单，其中包括担任财政部长的经济学家兼副总统恩达巴高拉特。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/botswana-s-president-picks-deputy-gaolathe-as-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 09:21:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相石破茂赢得决选，在可能与特朗普会面之前继续担任首相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/japan-s-pm-ishiba-faces-vote-to-keep-job-ahead-of-trump-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相石破茂收到了一些罕见的好消息，日本议会支持他留任，以便与美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普举行预期的重要会晤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/japan-s-pm-ishiba-faces-vote-to-keep-job-ahead-of-trump-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 00:10:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和马斯克在投票前权衡参议院领袖之争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/donald-trump-says-senate-s-next-leader-must-favor-recess-appointments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普和埃隆·马斯克向下一任参议院共和党领袖提出要求，这可能会打乱原本预计由米奇·麦康奈尔的长期盟友之一赢得的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/donald-trump-says-senate-s-next-leader-must-favor-recess-appointments</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 20:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
